Class Frame

  • java.lang.Object
    • funGUI.Frame
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Button, Calculator, Display, FunGUIFrame, ListItem, Message, NumOutput, Slider

    public abstract class Frame
extends java.lang.Object
    The frame class provides the basic structure of many of the interface classes, such as the way many objects are drawn to the screen.
